import React, { Component } from 'react'; import '../App.css'; import { Table } from 'reactstrap'; import TableHeader from './TableHeader'; class CycleA extends Component { render() { let load = (this.props.weight-this.props.bar); return (
A 40% 5x {Math.round(load*4/10).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*4/10).toFixed(1)}
B 50% 5x {Math.round(load*5/10).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*5/10).toFixed(1)}
C 60% 3x {Math.round(load*6/10).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*6/10).toFixed(1)}
1 65% 5x {Math.round(load*65/100).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*65/100).toFixed(1)}
2 75% 5x {Math.round(load*75/100).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*75/100).toFixed(1)}
2 85% 5x+ {Math.round(load*85/100).toFixed(1)} {Math.round(load/2*85/100).toFixed(1)}
) } } export default CycleA;
